Depends: libc6, libgcc-s1, libstdc++6, libx11-6, libxft2, libxrender1, libxrandr2, libxmu6, libjpeg62-turbo, libpng16-16, zlib1g, libcrypt1, libpam0g
Provides: x-display-manager
Section:  system
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://www.essora.org/
Description: Essora display manager based on Slim
 EssoraDM is a lightweight display manager for Essora.
 It is derived from Slim under GPL-2.0 and adds Essora naming,
 paths and boot splash hook integration.
